graph LR
    ODH[ODH Model Controller]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    ODH -->|watches CRDs<br/>creates resources| KServe[KServe v0.15.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|creates EnvoyFilters<br/>traffic routing| Istio[Istio v1.26.4<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|creates AuthPolicies<br/>authentication| Kuadrant[Kuadrant Operator v1.2.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|executes AuthPolicies<br/>authorization| Authorino[Authorino Operator v0.11.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|creates ServiceMonitors<br/>PodMonitors| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.76.2<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|creates Routes<br/>Templates| OpenShiftAPI[OpenShift API 4.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|creates HTTPRoutes<br/>Gateways| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1.2.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|watches Knative Services<br/>serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving<br/>v0.0.0-20250117084104<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    ODH -.->|creates TriggerAuthentications<br/>autoscaling| KEDA[KEDA v2.16.1<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODH -->|reads config<br/>feature flags| DSC[DSC/DSCI Operator<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    ODH -.->|registers models<br/>HTTP API| ModelRegistry[Model Registry v0.2.19<br/>INTERNAL ODH<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% External Services
    ODH -.->|validates accounts<br/>fetches models/secrets| NGC[NVIDIA NGC API<br/>EXTERNAL SERVICE<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Platform APIs
    ODH -->|watches CRDs<br/>creates resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>PLATFORM]

    %% Integration Points (components that use ODH Model Controller outputs)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management<br/>displays ISVCs| ODH
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models<br/>creates ISVCs| ODH
    Router[OpenShift Router] -.->|routes traffic<br/>uses Routes| ODH

    %% KServe dependencies (indirect)
    KServe -->|traffic management| Istio
    KServe -->|autoscaling| Knative

